snippet.title: Black Myth: WuKong - Official WeGame Event Trailer
snippet.description:
Black Myth: WuKong is a third-person action RPG developed by Game Science. Take a look at the latest trailer revealed at the WeGame Event showing off some new visuals, cutscenes, and gameplay from the upcoming Chinese mythology-rooted epic developed entirely in Unreal Engine 5. Black Myth: WuKong is launching on August 20 for PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series S|X, and PC.

#BlackMythWuKong #IGN #Gaming
